= Freedom Scoops Change Log
This is changelog to keep track of what is happing.

== General 

== Notes (8-25-2024) 
  ** Credit screen was added. And text was tweeked for the theme of project.
  ** Titepic folder was rename to screens and makefile was reworked for this as well.
  ** The Hero look was revamped. Even his face hud but only four for now.
  ** Hud got tweeked a little. Even placeholder hud font from red to some purple pink color.  
  ** Story and artwork concepts was add in misc folder to show what is planned so far.
  ** New resources was added and edited, three new weapons, some pickups, few new textures. etc... - ZNukem
  ** Manual info was mostly updated some text and names.
  ** A generated Playwad.sh file was included to make testing easier for Linux.
  ** Menu Bigfont color is turn to green and pink. Menu bar bit edited.
  ** A working in progess level for First Crunch, there also a mp level in same level. It should be chex quest compatible. - ZNukem
  ** This TODO was rename to ChangeLog. Real basic TODO was made list norrmal stuff. - ZNukem
  ** 6 & 7 weapon keys are fixed. Has been set back to norrmal in buildcfg.txt. Due to missunderstanding thinking mapset was shareware.
  ** Most of text was edited in FC1_.deh not all, rest of dehacked files stiil in works to edit.
  ** Dist folder content and names was changed still more work needs to be done.
  ** Main readme has been updated a little.

